{"tid":2353433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"攬炒巴屌臭重光團隊咁大件事冇人講？","createTime":"2021-01-04T17:36:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T01:53:52.000Z","uid":344464,"like":20,"dislike":65,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"e4fdf095343b6699936db12147209435f91da771","tid":2353433,"uid":344464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T17:36:46.000Z","msg":"「一個崩都無袋過之餘，啲支出仲係自己倒貼。重光團隊同人食飯會claim 錢，但係我兩袖清風從來無claim任何野，一個崩都無呀！<br />\n<br />\n重光團隊自己都承認全面控制1,600萬，佢地要hold錢、要推BNO，攬炒團隊同我10月已經無奈接受，由佢地。無資源就馬死落地行。<br />\n<br />\n但點L解唔問真正hold錢嘅重光做緊乜，走去屈鳩我有幾千萬洗？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n攬炒巴可唔可以講清楚少少重光團隊點樣挪用公款？點解亂用公款？你好明顯對佢哋有不滿喎，咁樣講兩句就算？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋咩叫由佢哋？咁撚順攤？"},{"pid":"ffb313dbf4417f85c7f1ae6f6bcef1d2df28d942","tid":2353433,"uid":344464,"like":5,"dislike":9,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T17:46:59.000Z","msg":"即係點呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"d19298d5416f8c52ac3bf378a2c5a5e415bd25d7","tid":2353433,"uid":374209,"like":15,"dislike":43,"score":-28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T17:51:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你好明顯啦 分唔到贓  本身叫攬炒巴咪幾好 眾籌一鋪大野 直接係泰晤士河買間豪宅   點撚樣知 無啦啦佢話俾人打 嗱佢話㗎咋 焗住開名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到個團隊要同佢分家  而家擺到明就係話想攞錢啦屌你 你聽唔到佢係咁話自己要貼錢咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74fc0ecb2cf2ff9838473b575daa32303f0b9c9c","tid":2353433,"uid":258356,"like":34,"dislike":11,"score":23,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T17:51:44.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">我屌你老母啦<br />\n<br />\n成堆黑警日鳩日抹黑完周梓樂<br />\n<br />\n同一堆accounts又有組織性地抹黑流亡人士<br />\n煩撚完未<br />\n<br />\n帶夠完方向未 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\"